column3:
<UIForeground>F201FC</UIForeground><UIGlow>F201FD</UIGlow> Quest Sync<UIGlow>01</UIGlow><UIForeground>01</UIForeground>
The troubled craftsman is in need of a helping hand.
Search for the missing pouch at Panaqpelu Retreat.
Deliver the missing pouch to the troubled craftsman.

Excuse me, <If(PlayerParameter(4))>miss<Else/>sir</If>, do you have a moment? Please, I need your help! I'm a craftsman come to discuss a new project with a client, but I seem to have lost my lucky charm along the way─my dear doll.
I'm afraid how the meeting may turn out without it... The last time I saw it was at Panaqpelu Retreat. Maybe it fell out when I was gathering my things.
I'm to meet with my client in just a moment, and it wouldn't do to be late. I realize this is sudden, but would you find my doll for me? I'll delay the meeting for as long as I can.
It should be inside a small pouch somewhere within the premises of Panaqpelu Retreat. Please find it for me, won't you?
You locate a small pouch behind the shelf. Inside you find an adorable doll, a warm smile adorning its face. This appears to be the missing item.
You open the lid and look inside the jar, but the doll is nowhere to be found within.
Were you able to find it?
Oh thank goodness, my precious doll! I won't let it out of my sight again!

We Pelupelu became merchants after Gulool Ja Ja bestowed a great kindness upon our people, to help achieve his goal of fostering amity between clans. This doll's bright smile serves as a reminder to uphold that ideal─to spread happiness through trade.
I've no doubt that you, being the kind-hearted individual that you are, will enjoy great fortune and happiness in your future business endeavors. I truly can't thank you enough for your help!
